<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Clubhouse | lAIdies</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="lAIdies is a Wednesday newsletter and community for women building practical AI fluency without pretending they have spare time."
    />
    <meta property="og:title" content="lAIdies | Girl power meets machine power" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="AI fluency for women with full calendars, high standards, and no patience for beige tech explanations." />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://wearelaidies.com/" />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://wearelaidies.com/assets/laidies-logo.png" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#ff2d9b" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="assets/laidies-logo-square.png" />
    <link rel="manifest" href="manifest.webmanifest" />
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="assets/laidies-logo-square.png" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css?v=issue-02-live-1" />
    <style>
      .clubhouse-menu { padding: clamp(24px, 4vw, 48px) clamp(18px, 5vw, 64px); }
      .clubhouse-menu h2 { font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.2vw, 2.4rem); margin-bottom: 6px; }
      .clubhouse-menu > p { color: #65515d; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 20px; }
      .clubhouse-menu-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
        gap: 14px;
      }
      .menu-card {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 4px;
        padding: 16px 18px;
        border: 2px solid #100805;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #100805;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #100805;
        background: #fff;
        transition: transform 150ms ease, box-shadow 150ms ease;
      }
      .menu-card:hover {
        transform: translate(-2px, -2px);
        box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 #100805;
      }
      .menu-card strong { font-size: 1rem; }
      .menu-card span { font-size: 0.82rem; color: #65515d; line-height: 1.4; }
      .menu-card em { font-size: 0.72rem; color: #247b83; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; margin-top: 4px; }
      @media (max-width: 560px) {
        .clubhouse-menu-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="site-header">
      <a class="brand" href="index.html" aria-label="lAIdies home">
        <img src="assets/laidies-logo-wordmark.png" alt="" />
      </a>
      <nav class="nav" aria-label="Primary navigation">
        <a href="episodes.html">Episodes</a>
        <a href="learn.html">Learn</a>
        <a href="clubhouse.html">Clubhouse</a>
        <a href="community.html">Community</a>
        <a href="this-week.html">This Week</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main id="top">
      <section class="page-intro" aria-labelledby="page-title">
        <p class="eyebrow">The Clubhouse</p>
        <h1 id="page-title">The break room for women who need a useful detour.</h1>
        <p>Games, card packs, advice from LAIDY, and the fun that also teaches you something. This is where you come when the spreadsheet can wait five minutes.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="clubhouse-menu" aria-labelledby="clubhouse-menu-title">
        <h2 id="clubhouse-menu-title">Pick your adventure.</h2>
        <p>Everything here is five minutes or less. Unless you get competitive about it.</p>
        <div class="clubhouse-menu-grid">
          <a href="#fun-games" class="menu-card">
            <strong>🎲 Games</strong>
            <span>Dream Phone career advice, Madame CLAI-O fortunes, Girl Talk prompts, and Cocktail Fortune.</span>
            <em>Play something → 5 min</em>
          </a>
          <a href="#member-passport" class="menu-card">
            <strong>💳 Your Clubhouse Pass</strong>
            <span>Build your member card. Track badges, quiz stickers, and card pulls.</span>
            <em>Set up → 3 min</em>
          </a>
          <a href="#card-pack" class="menu-card">
            <strong>🃏 Trading Cards</strong>
            <span>Flip, collect, and pin cards from each episode. New pack every Wednesday.</span>
            <em>Open a pack → 2 min</em>
          </a>
          <a href="#cocktailWheel" class="menu-card">
            <strong>🍸 Businesswomen's Special</strong>
            <span>Spin the wheel. Get a cocktail recipe matched to your current energy.</span>
            <em>Spin → 30 sec</em>
          </a>
          <a href="#madame-claio" class="menu-card">
            <strong>🔮 Madame CLAI-O</strong>
            <span>AI-powered career fortune readings. Practical advice, late-night-commercial drama.</span>
            <em>Get a reading → 1 min</em>
          </a>
          <a href="#dreamPhoneToggle" class="menu-card">
            <strong>📞 Dream Phone</strong>
            <span>Dial a number, pick a caller, get career and AI advice from the other end.</span>
            <em>Make a call → 3 min</em>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
